Reasoning: The paper deals with the analysis of Error Vector Magnitude (EVM) in an interference limited system with fading channels. This topic falls under the domain of Information Theory (cs.IT) and Communication (cs.COMM). The paper also discusses the impact of fading on EVM, which is a topic of interest in Signal Processing (cs.SI) and Numerical Analysis (cs.NA). Additionally, the paper uses special functions to simplify the derived EVM expressions, which is a topic of interest in Mathematics (cs.MA).
